Oh hello! Welcome to my selling journal. ( That sounded lameee. ) Anyway.

I have decided to put some things up for sale recently, so look around at your whimsy.
Shipping comes from the USA, so it shouldn't take too long for domestic orders.


I take paypal, money order, and us conceiled cash only. Well, that is quite a few options, so.. Heh. My contact address is soteniliene@gmail.com, and I will tell you my paypal account name if you email me. I am quick to respond, (thanks to gmail notifier, haha), so expect quick responses.

I expect to receive my money within 1 week of the order, unless you state otherwise, or keep me informed, I will remove your bid and comments.

Juicy Couture Velour Yellow Hoody Price: 11USD Size: USA Size Small Available Stock: 1. Category: Clothing Shipping: 4USD anywhere in the United States, 5USD International. Description: I bought this JUST because it was Juicy. It has the Juicy J for the zipper, and is made of yellow velour. It is totally pimp looking. Goes great with anything. Willing to haggle the price down, if needed. ( I will do pictures soon, I promise ) ROXY Light Blue Silk Night Clutch Price: 13USD Size: 10in wide by 6in high. Available Stock: 1. Category: Purse/Clutch Shipping: 4USD anywhere in the United States, 5USD International. Description: I bought this recently thinking that I would use it, and a lot. It is very very pretty. It has a clean front, with the ROXY name and symbol on a small silver peice in the bottom right corner. The top pulls up to reveal a small mirror on the top, and the purse on the bottom. Not very large, but perfect for going out. Has a small ( hardly noticeable, but I wanted to mention it) scratch across the silk blue front, causing a small .. shredding effect? You can't really see it unless you hunt for it. Comes with detachable, short handle.

Kah Doh Maru Price: 7USD Size: DVD and Case? Available Stock: 1 copy. Category: Anime Movie Shipping: 2USD anywhere in the United States, 3USD International. Description: I'm not sure what happened in this movie, but I remember that it was a fun movie to watch. It was short, though, only about an hour or so. It was stylized, and somewhat sad.. Comes with a mini-poster. DVD worn, but still very playable. Cowboy Bebop 3rd Session Price: 10USD Size: DVD and Case? Available Stock: 1 copy. Category: Anime Series Shipping: 2USD anywhere in the United States, 3USD International. Description: OMG, I hate to sell this, but it just sits around! It is kind of sad, I love this series to death. Which is why I want you to have it at a special discount. ( I bought it for like 19 dollars. ). I can adjust the price if you think this is a bit much. Mulan Special Edition Price: 9USD Size: DVD, Case & Outer cover. Available Stock: 1 copy. Category: Disney/Animated American Movie Shipping: 2USD anywhere in the United States, 3USD International. Description: I have watched this movie too many times to count. I can recite almost all songs in Chinese, English and French.. It is a good movie, and I bought this a LONG TIME AGO. So it has some wear. The Ring 2 Price: 7USD Size: DVD, Case & Outer cover. Available Stock: 1 copy. Category: Asian Horror Movie Shipping: 2USD anywhere in the United States, 3USD International. Description: I don't... really remember about this movie, so I will talk about the condition. The condition is great, the outside is like new and the disc is in great condition. No inside slips, sorry. I usually save those.. Haha. What Lies Beneath Price: 9USD Size: DVD, Case & Outer cover. Available Stock: 1 copy. Category: American Thriller Movie Shipping: 2USD anywhere in the United States, 3USD International. Description: I loved this movie, oddly enough. It has nothing to do with what I usually watch! Hilarious. Anyway, it is a thriller movie, and has some good actors in it. I have seen it several times, great condition.. The Mothman Prophecies Price: 7USD Size: DVD, Case & Outer cover. Available Stock: 1 copy. Category: American Thriller Movie Shipping: 2USD anywhere in the United States, 3USD International. Description: Did I even watch this? It is old, but in good condition. You should really watch it, and tell me about it. I think I started to watch it and got freaked out because I was all alone at home.. Haha. Has Richard Gere in it..

I am careful with my manga, but minor minor minor wears to the corners from being moved around and stuff. I am careful not to crease the covers when I open them. A few edges of the covers bent. Fairly old, my third manga book ever bought.. Trigun Volume One, Hardcover Price: 7USD Size: Manga-sized.. Available Stock: 1 copy. Category: Manga Shipping: 2USD anywhere in the United States, 3USD International. Description: Mint condition, or at least near that. I am careful with my manga, but minor minor minor wears to the corners from being moved around and stuff. I am careful not to crease the covers when I open them. It has a hard-cover, and I have the original book cover for it, which features full color artwork, texture-on-texture. I have read this a lot, it has to be my favourite manga by far. Vash is so cute.. ;_;, Anyway, seven dollars.. Inuyasha Volume One Price: 2USD Size: Manga-sized.. Available Stock: 1 copy. Category: Manga Shipping: 2USD anywhere in the United States, 3USD International. Description: Terrible quality. I am sorry, this book has been through a lot. That is why it is only two dollars. I don't want to throw it away, but I have had it since I was 12, thats about six years. A long time for a book, it was well loved and well lived. Not in terrible shape per-say on the pages, but the cover and advertisements have seen much better days. Love Hina Volume Four Price: 5USD Size: Manga-sized.. Available Stock: 1 copy. Category: Manga Shipping: 2USD anywhere in the United States, 3USD International. Description: Very good condition, near mint except for the fact that it is well-creased, edges worn a bit. Read and re-read hundreds of times, but still very much readable. I love this series. So cute and fun. BUY IT :D.
